OL,4,G1955FKirstie and Phil's Love It or
OL,5,     FList It
OL,6,     GIn the village of Clifford,
OL,7,     GKirstie and Phil meet Vic and
OL,8,     GPaul. From the outside, their
OL,9,     Gidyllic home looks perfect for a
OL,10,     Gfamily, but appearances can be
OL,11,     Gdeceptive.
OL,12,G2100FGrand Designs
OL,13,     GKara and Jonny build a stone and
OL,14,     Gzinc home in West Yorkshire's
OL,15,     Ghills, facing tough challenges.
OL,16,G2200F24 Hours in A&E
OL,17,     GAlyce, who's 89, is brought to
OL,18,     GKing's after falling near her
OL,19,     Ghome. Sean, who's 23, is rushed
OL,20,     Gin after having a seizure that's
OL,21,     Glasted most of the night.
